 essentially the same as the process related to transition bonds centerpoint energy restoration bond company llc was formed in  and issued system restoration bonds to recover the costs associated with restoring centerpoint energy houston’s distribution system following hurricane ike view details faqs print share nyse cnp    pm  jul     day high  day low   volume     delayed  min by esignal latest annual reports interactive  annual report  annual report  corporate responsibility report  form k  proxy statement corporate governance corporate structure investor news events  presentations financial information quarterly results annuals and proxies debt  maturities regulatory information sec filings transition and restoration bond companies centerpoint energy transition bond company ii llc sec filings semiannual servicers certificates centerpoint energy transition bond company llc transition bonds series  ratings assigned to the transition bonds series  remittances applications for trueup of transition charges quarterly statements on retail electric providers centerpoint energy transition bond company iii llc sec filings semiannual servicers certificates centerpoint energy transition bond company llc transition bonds series  ratings assigned to the transition bonds series  remittances applications for trueup of transition charges quarterly statements on retail electric providers centerpoint energy restoration bond company llc sec filings semiannual servicers certificates centerpoint energy restoration bond company senior secured system restoration bonds ratings assigned to senior secured system restoration bonds monthly remittances applications for trueup of restoration charges semiannual statements on retail electric providers centerpoint energy transition bond company iv llc sec filings semiannual servicers certificates centerpoint energy transition bond company iv  transition bonds ratings assigned to  senior secured transition bonds monthly remittances applications f